{
  "stem": "3721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I was saying-- is they were chasing me by bicycle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of them kept on continuously beating me, the, the Hungarian one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I fell numerous times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to somehow get up with my hands tied in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after we got to the synagogue-- that's where they were collecting all the Jews, as I said before, that they-- somebody put some kind of complaint.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Apparently, the non-Jewish community already had all their complaints submitted to somebody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because everybody knew somebody who they wanted to bring up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All you needed is not to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could put any complaint against anybody you wanted as long as the person that they put the complaint in was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, I got to this-- to the temple.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I hear this horrible screaming there already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there is an officer [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] turned around from me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the, the German officer goes over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he talks to this-- the German soldier, that is, goes over-- the SS trooper goes over to the officer, who was-- I didn't see because his back was to me-- and talks to him.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then the German officer turned around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he happened to be my classmate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [CRYING] he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was beaten up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the-- actually, the SS trooper asked permission that I should be taken to the cemetery and shot, dig my own-- he, he, he was-- he, he came with a shovel.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I should dig my own grave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he would shoot me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the German officer was a classmate, looked at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, leave this guy alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Let me-- let me do what I have to do with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
